meta.job_title: RPA Developer, Business Operations and Data Analytics

duties_responsibilities.duty: Collaborate with a cross-functional team to identify process inefficiencies and develop RPA solutions
Support, maintain, and provide process automation for cross-functional projects
Provide analytics and business process support for global financial operations
Stay up-to-date with developments in process automation

education_certification.credential: Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Engineering, Math, Finance, Statistics, or related discipline, or equivalent combination of education and experience
